#: ../../source/blog/magi_attn.md:390
msgid ""
"See the separate [blog post](./muon_qk_clip.md) for a technical description "
"of how we natively support **Muon QK-clip technique** in `Flex-Flash-"
"Attention` (kernel-level) and `MagiAttention` (distributed-level)."
msgstr ""
"关于我们如何在 `Flex-Flash-Attention`（内核级）和 `MagiAttention`（分布式级）中原生支持 **Muon QK-"
